<sect1 id="group__graph__cuda_1graph_functions">
<title>Available Functions</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacegraph__" kindref="compound">graph_</ref></computeroutput> namespace provides operations for graph neural network post-processing and analysis.</para>
