<sect1 id="group__graph__cuda_1graph_usage">
<title>Usage</title>
<para>These functions are typically used for post-processing GNN outputs:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;<ref refid="graph_8cuh" kindref="compound">graph/graph.cuh</ref>&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>After<sp/>GNN<sp/>forward<sp/>pass</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/><ref refid="enums_8h_1a71db5b98a8935886920bcc7eaaf49fb9aeaef5a1a889ab3d077c4cbb1bf789bf7" kindref="member">edge_index</ref><sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>[2,<sp/>E]</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>prediction<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>[E]<sp/>edge<sp/>predictions</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>features<sp/>=<sp/>...;<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>[N,<sp/>F]<sp/>node<sp/>features</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>result<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="namespacegraph___1a7249186f32a05a8ff1601bff5deabdef" kindref="member">graph_::edge_aggregation</ref>(<ref refid="enums_8h_1a71db5b98a8935886920bcc7eaaf49fb9aeaef5a1a889ab3d077c4cbb1bf789bf7" kindref="member">edge_index</ref>,<sp/>prediction,<sp/>features);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">torch::Tensor<sp/>aggregated<sp/>=<sp/>result[</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;aggregated&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">];</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</sect1>
